mixin post(src)
  .post-blog
    a.link-primary--clear.link(href='#')
      .post-head
        a.link-primary--clear.link(href='#')
          h3.title-xl.c-tertiary Titulo do post
      .row
        .col-md-4.mb-4
          a.link-primary--clear.link(href='#')
            img.img-fluid(src=src, alt="")
        .col-md-8.mb-4
          a.link-primary--clear.link(href='#') Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolorem dolorum libero eos veritatis delectus et ipsum non maxime iure? Voluptatum tempore eius quidem inventore eos. Distinctio alias harum voluptatem! Quod.
    .post-footer
      small Publicado em
